name: Goodbye 2021
description:
In my opinion, 2021 is the most impressive year in my life, this year I was able to find a warm family even though I have never spoken to anyone, plunged into the world of NFT. And I hope that next year we can be better.
This work is my last work at NFT 2021. See you next time. this is End but not finished. Thank you 2021
